text.tspan: MDG5.B: Share of married women using contraceptives, 1990 to 2013
Millennium Development Goal (MDG) 5.B was to ensure universal access to contraceptives for all. This is measured as
the share of women who were married or in a union using contraceptives. This target was not achieved.

text.textPath: Target: Universal access to contraceptives for women
